title: [Xandrya's Outfitting]
[Xandrya's Magic Shoppe]
description: Enclosed by tightly-woven beige canvas walls, the shop features an elegantly woven reed mat in the center of its dark oak floor.  A multihued Vornavian silk tapestry hangs under the light oak ceiling.  Right near the front is a set of carved felwood shelves.
